Scavenger Major Update:
- Scavenger Pawns (using HAR)
- Scavenger faction (consisting of Scav Pawns)
- Blue lizards
- Monks planting a karma flower on death (1% chance)

Pack Minor Update:
- Slugcats can become pack animals
- All lizard types can become pack animals
- Fixing dessicated lizard textures

Anomaly Minor Update:
- Add support for anomaly, making use of the new hostility XML node
- Allow DLL and BLL to be captured as research entities
- Change meat type to twisted meat

Undetermined Minor Update:
- Slugcats can use a variety of weapons
- Fixing lizard UI icon
- Use hediff sprites to reflect hediffs on the sprite